>\n<br />\n根據美國憲法，總統作為三軍總司令，是唯一擁有授權使用核武的人，不需要取得軍事顧問或國會的同意發動核攻擊，軍方或國會亦無法推翻相關決定。有美媒質疑佩洛西今次的處理手法，認為這不但引起公眾恐慌，亦令特朗普關注自己對核武使用的權力，也使國防部陷入困境。白宮及國防部暫未回應事件。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"唔係要兩件先可以開動到核武咩...."},{"pid":"15c60ac7d5eb8480831807ccb8f3771163c03f4b","tid":2359280,"uid":58670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"22e25f4a1ab5dbf83752b46f4e0f93bed1e3a956","tid":2359280,"uid":259777,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:37:39.000Z","msg":"如果侵突然發難要射核武嘅話會射去邊個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"加州，紐約，華盛頓對付deep state <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda8801d0fbbf5eca10a2050b7ec8b8fca6cfaa2","tid":2359280,"uid":291465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"點解要咁驚隻落水狗，唔爭在果十零日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13d911d02d74f93a6f6c5015b1cc150e0aa67f8","tid":2359280,"uid":61831,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c45025c6ef42a004f7ad1bf9c6d79f73f349ce8a","tid":2359280,"uid":89182,"like":7,"dislike":39,"score":-32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:41:48.000Z","msg":"淨係「精神失常的總統」已經踩到愛侵力條尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:19:00.000Z","msg":"係唔係愛侵力都會覺得有問題啦，依家佢比精神科醫生確認左精神失常？"},{"pid":"deff79b0350f51c4884aeb489fbd3138e34b9805","tid":2359280,"uid":24745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c45025c6ef42a004f7ad1bf9c6d79f73f349ce8a","tid":2359280,"uid":89182,"like":7,"dislike":39,"score":-32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T18:41:48.000Z","msg":"淨係「精神失常的